{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|小|隹|t1=small|t2=bird|ls=ic}} – a small bird, a sparrow.

In the current form, the upper part looks like {{zh-l|*少}}, but what looks like the bottom stroke of {{lang|zh|少}} is actually the upper left stroke of {{lang|zh|隹}}, extended.

